{"word":"Hagar","slug":"hagar","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hagar</b> <a href=\"#/H1904\">H1904</a><br/><a href=\"#/G28\">G28</a> <br/> A servant of Abraham and handmaid of Sarah.<br/> Given by Sarah to Abraham to be his wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16'>Gen 16</a><br/> Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=15'>Gen 25:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=10'>1Ch 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=22'>1Ch 5:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=83&verse=6'>Psa 83:6</a><br/> Called Agar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=4&verse=25'>Gal 4:25</a>"}]}